      <title>中国暗示流动性方在着眼于增长方面存在局限性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/china-cautions-on-liquidity-party-taking-fuel-off-growth-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国向几个月来一直在现金池中游泳的银行家发出了一个意外的提醒，即其流动性增加的目的是振兴经济，而不是帮助支持金融投机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/china-cautions-on-liquidity-party-taking-fuel-off-growth-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 08:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
